import { Container, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap'
import CategoryBar from '../components/CategoryBar.js'
import BrandBar from '../components/BrandBar.js'
import ProductList from '../components/ProductList.js'

const Shop = () => {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Row className="mt-2">
                <Col md={3}>
                    <CategoryBar />
                </Col>
                <Col md={9}>
                    <BrandBar />
                    <ProductList />
                </Col>
            </Row>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Shop
